```

### Response with Code
```json
{
  "content": "Found the function in auth-service.js",
  "attachment": {
    "type": "CODE",
    "data": {
      "file": "auth-service.js",
      "snippet": "function authenticate(token) {...}",
      "lines": "45-48"
    }
  },
  ...
}
```

